---
title: Sichuan Glazed Pork Meatballs with Udon Noodles & Crispy Shallots
description: This saucy noodle number puts a tasty Asian twist on meatballs and spaghetti. Tender pork meatballs and sweet capsicum are coated in a mouth-watering Sichuan garlic glaze, with a sprinkling of crispy shallots for crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dc352990b95b65cd471250b-ec2f4dff.jpg
